<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS, if IPI request to ASU is sent successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XASU_INVALID_ARGUMENT, if any argument is invalid.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XASU_INVALID_UNIQUE_ID, if received Queue ID is invalid.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE, if sending an IPI request to ASU fails. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
